## Proposed Architecture

### 1. Database Models (`backend/app/models/assets.py`)

**Model: `Asset`**
- `id` (UUID)
- `name` (String)
- `category` (Enum: Financial, Business, Physical, Personal)
- `description` (Text)
- `status` (Enum: Idea, Research, Planning, In Progress, Under Development, Acquired, Active, Generating Income, Completed, Archived)
- `target_completion_date` (Date)
- `expected_cost` (Decimal)
- `actual_invested` (Decimal)
- `expected_value` (Decimal)
- `expected_monthly_income` (Decimal)
- `actual_monthly_income` (Decimal)
- `priority` (Enum: Low, Medium, High, Critical)
- `project_id` (UUID, Foreign Key to `projects.id` for Roadmap integration)

**Model: `AssetIdea` (Opportunity Vault)**
- `id` (UUID)
- `title` (String)
- `estimated_cost` (Decimal)
- `estimated_time_months` (Int)
- `potential_roi_percent` (Decimal)
- `risk_level` (Enum: Low, Medium, High)
- `priority` (Enum: Low, Medium, High)
- `notes` (Text)
- `research_links` (Text/JSON)

### 2. Asset Scoring System

The backend will compute an `asset_score` (1-100) on the fly (or via a DB property) based on an algorithmic weighting of:
- ROI Potential
- Income Potential
- Scalability (We can add a `scalability` 1-10 field to the Asset table)
- Risk (Inversely proportional)
- Time Required (Inversely proportional)
- Capital Required (Inversely proportional)

### 3. API Routers (`backend/app/api/v1/assets.py`)
- `GET /api/v1/assets/dashboard` (Aggregates Total Asset Value, Future Value, Passive Income, Growth Trend)
- `CRUD /api/v1/assets`
- `CRUD /api/v1/asset-ideas`

